HealthLynked maintains a healthcare provider and practice directory used by patients to search for doctors, practices, specialties, locations, phone numbers, and other provider-related information.<br>
The problem is that healthcare provider data changes constantly:<br>
вАҐ    Providers move to new practices<br>
вАҐ    Practices close, merge, or rebrand<br>
