p>Design or prototype a repeatable AI-powered pipeline that can help HealthLynked keep its provider and practice directory updated.</p>
<p>The system should be able to:</p>
<ol>
<li>Identify provider and practice records that may be outdated.</li>
<li>Search reliable public and legally accessible sources for updated information.</li>
<li>Compare existing HealthLynked data against external sources.</li>
<li>Normalize provider names, practice names, addresses, phone numbers, specialties, and affiliations.</li>
<li>Detect potential duplicates, inactive providers, moved providers, and practice changes.</li>
<li>Assign a confidence score to each proposed update.</li>
<li>Automatically approve high-confidence updates.</li>
<li>Send uncertain or conflicting records to human review.</li>
<li>Maintain an audit trail of what changed, why it changed, and which sources supported the change.</li>
<li>Keep cost low by avoiding unnecessary paid APIs, unnecessary LLM calls, and unnecessary manual review.<br>
We are not looking for one-time manual data cleanup. We are looking for a repeatable data pipeline that can run continuously or periodically.</li>
</ol></div></div></div></div></div><div id="submission-requirements" class="sc-bBwdJu"><div class="sc-efsgwo gbmUJs sc-cPwvPg PqZRy"><div class="sc-cTZdpT dZqWIt"><div id="Submission Requirements" class="sc-dUWfqu erEATP"><div class="sc-hUxjbq kfDPZz"><div class="sc-fJhHEt bxzGtZ"><div class="sc-cRSGRE bjhwTM"><h3 class="sc-iqkkDd sc-lgGiis kpzoPI bRLVMl">Submission Requirements</h3></div></div><button aria-label="Copy link" title="Copy link" class="sc-iBjNZB ewthWL google-symbols notranslate">link</button></div></div><button aria-label="Collapse " title="Collapse " class="sc-iBjNZB ewthWL google-symbols notranslate" aria-expanded="true" style="flex-shrink: 0;">keyboard_arrow_up</button></div><div><div class="sc-kVpnwf cYyCew"><div class="sc-dFBygw goGFMn"><p>What Participants Can Submit<br>
